<abstract>New York City Green Infrastructure, 2025 is a point theme representing the locations and detailed information of green infrastructure practices in NYC neighborhoods built primarily through NYC Green Infrastructure Program initiatives as of 2025. Columbia library staff accessed this data in April of 2026 from the NYC Open Data portal at https://data.cityofnewyork.us/Environment/DEP-Green-Infrastructure-Point-Layer-/df32-vzax/about_data and has provided it in the geopackage format. A codebook is included in the full download package.
		</abstract>
